## 3.2 Decision Record Format

```markdown
## DECISION-{number}: {title}
- **Level**: S/A/B/C
- **Role**: [role code]
- **Problem**: {the issue requiring a decision}
- **Options**: 
  - A: {option A}
  - B: {option B}
- **Decision**: {final choice}
- **Rationale**: {why this was chosen}
- **Date**: {YYYY-MM-DD}
- **Status**: PENDING / CONFIRMED / REVISED
```

